## Not yet specified

- GitHub + Twitter ingress (no webhooks today — pull adapters? new hooks?
  hangs on the ingress research).
- ClickHouse "pings": the observer periodically reading telemetry for
  anomaly observations (system self-awareness pages) — shape unclear until
  the epoch model lands.
- Cross-source dedup (same event arriving via Slack AND GitHub AND Front).
- Whether stream observations get their own Brain section or share
  `observations/` with a `source:` field.

## Out of scope

- Editorial (editions, open-loop presentation) — the Bugle keeps it; this
  map feeds it.
- Sending/replying/acting on any stream — read-only forever, per standing
  law.
- Public access to anything.
